name: ITelliSource (I•tell•la•source)
body:
### Welcome to ITelliSource
This is the central reference point for the various open source projects that have been created by ITelliTech and @SpiderMatt3825U. General information and new release announcements will be maintained here as well as basic information on the various projects that are available for use.

### Content Coming Soon!
The content for this general information and announcement hub will be published as soon as additional free time is available for contributing to this project. Until then, if you would like further information or have any questions or concerns, please send an email to info@itellitech.org.
